New on the Market! PERFECT FOR DEVELOPMENT! TOTAL 26.02 ACRES. (5 separate MLS #s) All Properties being sold by different sellers and only will be sold together. This site is a wonderful opportunity for development and is located adjacent to The Reserve in Wake Forest. All utilities including natural gas are assessable to the property. Please see map in documents for overview of available properties being sold.
From Raleigh, Exit Hwy 98 Bypass - Calvin Jones Hwy., Turn left onto Traditions Grande Blvd. Go 1/6 miles, destination is on your right.
